{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Loaders</h1>\n<p>loaders are used when retrieving data or performing slow computations, and help to notify users\nthat loading is underway.</p>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<p>loaders has 2 sizes <code>c-loader--small</code> and <code>c-loader--large</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--small<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--large<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>loaders on white background</h3>\n<p>You can apply it using the <code>c-loader--white-container</code> modifier class</p>\n<div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex--row u-align-items--center u-window-padding--1x\">\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--small\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--1x\">small loader</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--large\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--2x\">large loader</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--small<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>loaders on dark background</h3>\n<p>use it by apply the <code>c-loader--dark-container</code> modifier class</p>\n<div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex--row u-align-items--center u-bg-blue u-window-padding--1x\">\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--small c-loader--dark-container\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--1x u-color-white\">small loader</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--large c-loader--dark-container\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--2x u-color-white\">large loader</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--large c-loader--dark-container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>loaders on light background</h3>\n<div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex--row u-align-items--center u-bg-ink-opacity-6 u-window-padding--1x\">\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--small c-loader--light-container\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--1x\">small loader</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--center\">\n    <div class=\"c-loader c-loader--large c-loader--light-container\"></div>\n    <span class=\"u-left-margin--2x\">large loader</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<h3>Modifiers</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Class</th>\n<th>Usage</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>c-loader--large</code></td>\n<td>use large loader size - 32px x 32px</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>c-loader--small</code></td>\n<td>use small loader size - 16px x 16px</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","frontmatter":{"title":"Loaders"}}},"pageContext":{"pathSlug":"/docs/loaders"}}